title: Nicki Minaj flashes underboob in bikini on Miami Beach set
text:
Nicki Minaj flashed the trendy new cleavage - underboob - on the Miami Beach set of the music video for Make Love on Monday.
The 34-year-old rap diva was dressed in little more than a bedazzled bikini, body chain, hoop earrings, fur coat, and gladiator heels.
The 10-time Grammy nominee is rumoured to be romancing the shoot's videographer, Grizz Lee aka Alex Loucas.

Letting it all hang out: The 34-year-old rap diva was dressed in little more than a bedazzled bikini, body chain, hoop earrings, fur coat, and gladiator heels
Labor of love? The 10-time Grammy nominee is rumoured to be romancing the shoot's videographer, Grizz Lee aka Alex Loucas
Joining Nicki (born Onika Maraj) for the scantily-clad clip was Grammy-nominated rapper Future.
Minaj and the ex-fiancé of Ciara (born Nayvadius Wilburn) also tooled around in a fancy white convertible.
In a behind-the-scenes video, 33-year-old Future mentioned they were shooting at a 'secret location' which might have been the Versace Mansion (Casa Casuarina).

Missing from Florida was the Bom Bidi Bom rapper's Make Love partner - Gucci Mane - who was in Manhattan filming his appearance on The Tonight Show.
The Trinidad-born, New York-raised beauty's trap track with the 37-year-old Georgian (born Radric Davis) is already available for download.
